{"id": "1511592648870461611", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "- mulligan everything but helot arachne strikes, wheel/posses, corpo enhance, and winkle 4c\n\n- must burst with mpreg wheel on helot, corpo enhance is really strong too\n\n- helot skills, exalts other than helot arachne not needed, although the 0c for 3, 1c skill tends to be positive if you don't play too early\n\n- blue ringed on whoever likely to exalt, this can be based off strikes, can be placed after blue ring toxin", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T04:49:31.524000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Pollux_gift", "emoji_id": "1459081694148558943", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1511592977473081445", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "- encounter you would like to save when you have the most cards in hand for the most value", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T04:50:49.869000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1511593144553177189", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "sometimes you save the winkle taunt because you need it in case there's a stun, weakness, or assassin (ex. ogier + ghelot i definitely did not lose to this)", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T04:51:29.704000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-03T05:07:17.673000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Pollux_gift", "emoji_id": "1459081694148558943", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1511593468798173205", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "when you are helot exalting try to save as many cards as you can, unless you want to ping a barrier, apply vuln, or play helot skills to gain charge", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T04:52:47.010000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Pollux_gift", "emoji_id": "1459081694148558943", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1511594097863950498", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 0, "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "author_bot": false, "content": "you usually do not need to play the double play arachne skill but it can be nice if they are weakening your aliemus gen somehow", "timestamp": "2026-06-03T04:55:16.991000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Pollux_gift", "emoji_id": "1459081694148558943", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
